                            <p>In cloud-based and AI-driven environments, these systems leverage speech recognition, natural language processing (NLP), and real-time data integration. As conversations occur, Agent Assist tools analyze spoken or typed input to retrieve relevant knowledge base content, past ticket data, or next-best actions. Script Guidance adapts dynamically based on dialogue, ensuring consistency and regulatory compliance. These tools are embedded within unified agent desktops alongside Customer Relationship Management (CRM), ticketing, and quality systems. Post-call, they generate interaction summaries and recommend coaching points to support continuous learning.</p>
